The evidence with the title 'Older americans oppose age tax in health care bill ' says Mar 21, 2017  ... The vast majority of older Americans , including those who voted for president Donald Trump , are opposed to the “ age tax ” in the proposed American Health Care Act ( AHCA ) , which would hike the cost of health insurance for people over age 50.That is a key finding of a poll of 605 Americans over age 50  ... 
